title: Fort White rushes for 356, stampedes past Baldwin
text:
Fort White rushes for 356, stampedes past Baldwin 
Sat, Oct 3, 2015 @ 12:17 am 
FORT WHITE 35 
BALDWIN 0 
Corey Dryden gained 112 yards on 16 carries, leading Fort White’s ground game in a rout of visiting Baldwin (1-4, 0-2 District 6-1A). ... Jacquez Pelham added to the rushing attack with 86 yards and two TDs, while Don Robinson ran for 83 yards and two more scores. ... Fort White (3-2, 1-0) outrushed Baldwin 356 yards to 25 and gained 21 first downs to Baldwin’s five.
